results.name: Denominators of resistance values < 1 ohm that can be obtained from a network of exactly 5 one-ohm resistors, but not from any network with fewer than 5 one-ohm resistors. Numerators are in A338580.
example: The list of the 20 = A051389(5) resistance values, sorted by increasing size of R = A338580(n)/a(n) = A338605(n)/A338600(5) is [1/5, 2/7, 3/8, 3/7, 4/7, 5/8, 5/7, 4/5, 5/6, 6/7] and the reciprocal resistances > 1 ohm [7/6, 6/5, 5/4, 7/5, 8/5, 7/4, 7/3, 8/3, 7/2, 5/1].
results.author: _Hugo Pfoertner_, Nov 03 2020
